title: Call St. Francis Arms Home! Lovely 1-Bedroom Home Available!
posting_body: ['St. Francis Arms', 'Address:', '739 East El Camino Real Sunnyvale, CA 94087', '1D  1 \xa0bed / 1 bath / 725 Sq.', 'Ft / $2,950 - $2,970', '* Unit 624 - Available 08/09/22', '* Unit 629 - Available 09/29/22', '* Unit 641 - Available 10/25/22', 'Serenity in Sunnyvale', 'Coming home to St. Francis Arms is the best part, your own personal escape far from the hustle and bustle.', "Walk around and you'll see folks out walking their dogs, birds chirping about, fishing swimming in the vast pond.", 'Neighbors are treated to two pools, as well as a fitness center outfitted with treadmills, weights, and both elliptical and cardiovascular equipment.', 'Visit our property right away.', 'Floor Plan Specials', '1 Month Free on Select Apartments', 'Property Amenities:', '* OnsiteMaintenance', '* Sundeck', '*', 'FitnessCenter', '* Pool', '* Availability24Hours', '* OnSiteManagement', '* CoverPark', '* RecRoom', '* NightPatrol', '* Transportation', '* ShortTermLease', '* SmokeFree', '* Garage', '* Laundry', 'Lease Terms:', 'Variable', 'Parking:', 'Covered parking, garage and carport available.', 'Please call us for more information.', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cat, Dog s are allowed.', 'We welcome up to 3 pets per household with a $200 per pet deposit and $65 per pet monthly pet rent.', 'Cats and dogs are welcomed without weight restrictions though certain breed restrictions apply.', 'Please call our leasing office for more details on our pet policy.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', ':\u2002\u2002 9:00am to 5:00pm', 'Management Company:', 'Prometheus Real Estate Group, Inc.*', 'Call Us Today!', 'show contact info', 'x543', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
